snippet.title: CLAP HANZ GOLF Trailer w/ Gameplay | Apple Arcade
snippet.description:
Subscribe for more game trailers 👉 http://bit.ly/mustachegamer

Clap Hanz, the company behind PlayStation system staples like Everybody’s Golf and Hot Shots Golf, has its own original game on Apple Arcade called Clap Hanz Golf. As you might imagine, it’s a similar sort of experience. It is immediately available for subscribers and can be played with or without a controller. 

#CLAPHANZGOLF #Golf # CLAPHANZGOLAppleArcade

⭐ The most anticipates games coming out in 2021: https://youtu.be/Ju3oIIqAv6Y
